Class ProtectedProperty.ValueSetter<V>

  • java.lang.Object

    ProtectedProperty<V>

    public static class ProtectedProperty.ValueSetter<V>
extends java.lang.Object
    A secret used to set the value of a protected property. A setter can be paired with at most one target property and if reused any previous pairing will be lost.
